{"id": 1195, "genre": 1001, "title": "职场中的性别偏见，你见过哪些？", "description": "女生时不时觉得自己受到了歧视，男生呢？（题图来自：Kiki Ljung）", "record_count": 2581, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160830153041YQMonSrFaOtCJ97D.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-18T03:00:44Z", "options": [{"id": 117379, "content": "怎么还没弄完，是男人吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272586}, {"id": 117415, "content": "讨论这个问题本身就有偏见吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 608116}, {"id": 111742, "content": "女生工作稍微努力一点，就被认为是无趣的“女强人”", "image": null, "praise_count": 195, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 117376, "content": "男人吸烟是帅是酷是理所应该，是被原谅；女人抽烟是颓废是放纵是自甘堕落、自怜自哀，是被异样眼光所看待。", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 762483}, {"id": 117386, "content": "还好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 553623}, {"id": 117405, "content": "男生...就多干点???", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667933}, {"id": 117406, "content": "我是女生，所以.......?    到底是自己歧视自己，还是别人歧视你?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667933}, {"id": 136201, "content": "产假只放女生导致用人单位不喜欢用女生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843361}, {"id": 117516, "content": "公司应聘的时候看到是二十五以上的女性都会直接无视，这公平吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751712}, {"id": 117517, "content": "已婚未育的面试会不通过", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319861}, {"id": 121618, "content": "给女性某些特权", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773447}, {"id": 117528, "content": "女记者/专栏作者/编辑适合时尚健康亲子星座教育娱乐，不适合时政社会经济户外体育。什么？比较专业的心理文章和严肃影评？女人逻辑思维不行......于是放着我一个心理学专业的人去报道社团活动，让学会计出身的男同事负责抑郁症专题，我还能说什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753890}, {"id": 125488, "content": "评论里有些直男癌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800573}, {"id": 118328, "content": "哈哈哈还哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711718}, {"id": 182593, "content": "挣钱比男的多，被嘲讽", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978742}, {"id": 121419, "content": "讨厌面试的时候，看到是女生直接pass！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 779427}, {"id": 121190, "content": "三八节。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 778065}, {"id": 118121, "content": "财务很难相处，领导都同意了，还是每次报销时求奶奶告爷爷的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766837}, {"id": 121705, "content": "有传统的面试官接受不了我是个T", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 784351}, {"id": 171882, "content": "目前在银行工作，被全家逼着考公务员。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949444}, {"id": 118132, "content": "漂亮女人的高职位是跟老板睡出来的！漂亮女人就只适合接待！漂亮女人谈业务不被重视！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766837}, {"id": 111735, "content": "“女的当男的用，男的当牲口用”到底是歧视女性还是男性？", "image": null, "praise_count": 448, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 171389, "content": "总是优先提拔男性", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 909399}, {"id": 111741, "content": "女生多的团队被怀疑八卦多、合作差", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 117374, "content": "女生每个月有姨妈假，春节期间只留男性值班...", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283771}, {"id": 117375, "content": "女的要生孩子要结婚，说的好像男的不结婚，不陪产似的", "image": null, "praise_count": 172, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726824}, {"id": 117631, "content": "本人是土木学院的女生，平时老师讲职业规划都针对性面向男生。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 764372}, {"id": 130688, "content": "面试时聊的挺好的，然后被问到星座了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219791}, {"id": 119681, "content": "会计师事务所对男生要求低", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769637}, {"id": 117378, "content": "女性开发不如男程序员，女性只适合干精细的体力劳动", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 86691}, {"id": 117380, "content": "女人那么拼事业干嘛。\n\n老娘乐意，管得着吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 257, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 122757, "content": "女孩子过了25了，就是剩女了，科科", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755093}, {"id": 117382, "content": "招聘的时候 男女不限 但女性要结了婚的", "image": null, "praise_count": 160, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 762078}, {"id": 117384, "content": "中高层基本都是男性；hr、财务基本是女性", "image": null, "praise_count": 144, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673453}, {"id": 117385, "content": "达到生育年龄的女性，一律不招聘", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480284}, {"id": 121737, "content": "学小语种的女生 再努力 也抵不过“性别男”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 784961}, {"id": 111755, "content": "说不要让女生晚回去了，男生留下来加班吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 190, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 117387, "content": "我觉得……这个问题很重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 553623}, {"id": 117388, "content": "追求完全的平等是做不到的，只有追求个别的不平等才有戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410755}, {"id": 117389, "content": "大概就是怀孕之类的吧?", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253159}, {"id": 117392, "content": "有时候技术一面试看见是女的就默认pass\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753586}, {"id": 117393, "content": "面试的时候女生拿出一纸不孕证明比别的证书都有用", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493631}, {"id": 117394, "content": "巴拉这个巴拉那个，总有一句：你是男人嘛？\r\n发工资发奖金的时候，也来一句你是男人嘛？\r\n怪我遇到的同事太奇葩喽，傻白甜小说电视剧看多了吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1403}, {"id": 118163, "content": "女仔稳主好人家嫁左米得咯，咩都五洗愁了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741508}, {"id": 117396, "content": "女人有份轻松稳定的工作就行了，将来方便照顾孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518134}, {"id": 117399, "content": "XX岗位，限女或限男", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658054}, {"id": 117400, "content": "女性认为职场上被歧视，但是根据匿名调查，女性更不乐意做工作上的「苦活累活」", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 367664}, {"id": 117401, "content": "职场男人不顾家，但调查显示职场女性更不顾家", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 367664}, {"id": 117402, "content": "女的可以随意发嗲卖萌聊八卦，起码在人际交往上男性会差很多！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 762305}, {"id": 117403, "content": "本公司只招收男员工", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511375}]}